{{use mdy dates|date=December 2012}} {{more citations needed|date=December 2012}} {{Infobox recurring event | name = Insubordination Fest | logo = <!--INCLUDE "[[File:Filename.ext]]" when entering file name--> | logo_caption = | image = The Dopamines 5 (4738783456).jpg | imagesize = | caption = The Dopamines | alt = | date = Summer | begins = | ends = | frequency = Annual | location = [[Baltimore]], [[Maryland]], United States | years_active = Since {{start date and age|2006}} | first = <!--"founded=" also works--> | last = | participants = Musicians | attendance = | genre = [[Punk-rock]], [[Pop-punk]], [[Power pop]] | budget = | organized = [[Insubordination Records]] | website = | footnotes = }}
'''Insubordination Fest''' is an American annual [[punk rock]] music festival held in [[Baltimore]], [[Maryland]], that usually takes place over three days, in late June.
The festival started in 2006 as a tenth-anniversary showcase for [[Insubordination Records]],<ref>Justin (April 2, 2006). [http://www.punknews.org/article/16632 "Insubordination Records 10th anniversary Festival"]. Punknews.org. Retrieved December 12, 2012.</ref> and has been held every summer since. In the past, the festival has been headlined by bands such as [[Dillinger Four]], [[Less Than Jake]], [[The Mr. T Experience]], [[The Queers]] and [[Teenage Bottlerocket]].
