'''North American Cystic Fibrosis Conference''' ('''NACFC''') The NACFC is an annual conference. It is a medical/scientific forum designed for attendance by health care professionals and research scientists involved with [[cystic fibrosis]]. The goal of the conference is to further the mission of the [[Cystic Fibrosis Foundation]] by creating a forum for open dialog and sharing of information among health care professionals.
